data.text:
Josip Broz Tito was a Yugoslav communist revolutionary and statesman, serving in various positions of national leadership from 1943 until his death in 1980.

He fought Hahciman in the Round 4 of Ragnarok.

Appearance[]

Tito is an average-height beardless man with a form of a young muscular man. He has a black slicked back hair and grey eyes.

Tito wears a Austro-Hungarian Army attire with gloves, and is helmetless.

Personality[]

Tito is smug has he doesn't show any fear to anyone, however during the battle he is very serious which he stayed focused.

Abilities[]

Golden Age: As a Human soul in the afterlife, Tito possesses the appearance and skills that he had during his Golden Age, the age in which he was at his peak.

Techniques[]

Ultimate Death: .

Equipment[]

Mondragón rifle: A Divine Weapon in the form of a rifle provided by the Völundr of the th Valkyrie, .

Plot[]

See Josip Broz Tito vs Hachiman for complete informations.

Trivia[]

During WW1, Tito was the youngest sergeant major in Austro - Hungarian Army.
